 IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
 PROGRAM-ID. READSEQ2.
******************************************************************
 ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
******************************************************************
 INPUT-OUTPUT SECTION.
 FILE-CONTROL.
     SELECT IN-FILE ASSIGN TO SEQ
     ORGANIZATION IS SEQUENTIAL.
******************************************************************
 DATA DIVISION.
******************************************************************

 FILE SECTION.
 FD IN-FILE
     RECORD CONTAINS 80 CHARACTERS.
 01 IN-RECORD.
     05 PERSON-DOB.
        10 PERSON-YEAR    PIC 9999.
        10 PERSON-MONTH   PIC 99.
        10 PERSON-DAY     PIC 99.
     05 PERSON-NAME       PIC A(15).
     05 PERSON-COUNTRY    PIC A(10).
**********************************
 WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
**********************************
 01 SWITCHES.
     05 EOF-SWITCH        PIC X VALUE "N".
 01 COUNTERS.
     05 REC-COUNTER       PIC 9(3) VALUE 0.
 77 WS-DOB                PIC X(10).
 77 WS-POS                PIC S9(3) VALUE 1.
******************************************************************
 PROCEDURE DIVISION.
******************************************************************
 000-MAIN.
     PERFORM 100-INITIALISE.
     PERFORM 200-PROCESS-RECORDS
         UNTIL EOF-SWITCH = "Y".
     PERFORM 300-TERMINATE.
**********************************
     STOP RUN.
**********************************
 100-INITIALISE.
**********************************
     OPEN INPUT IN-FILE.
     READ IN-FILE
         AT END MOVE "Y" TO EOF-SWITCH
         NOT AT END COMPUTE REC-COUNTER = REC-COUNTER + 1
     END-READ.
**********************************
 200-PROCESS-RECORDS.
**********************************
     MOVE 1 TO WS-POS.
     STRING
            PERSON-DAY   DELIMITED BY SIZE
            '/'          DELIMITED BY SIZE
            PERSON-MONTH DELIMITED BY SIZE
            '/'          DELIMITED BY SIZE
            PERSON-YEAR  DELIMITED BY SIZE
     INTO WS-DOB
     WITH POINTER WS-POS.
     DISPLAY 'NAME   : ' PERSON-NAME
     DISPLAY 'COUNTRY: ' PERSON-COUNTRY
     DISPLAY 'DOB    : ' WS-DOB
     READ IN-FILE
         AT END MOVE "Y" TO EOF-SWITCH
         NOT AT END COMPUTE REC-COUNTER = REC-COUNTER + 1
     END-READ.
**********************************
 300-TERMINATE.
**********************************
     DISPLAY 'TOTAL RECORDS: ' REC-COUNTER.
     CLOSE IN-FILE.
